    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I cannot believe what I am reading. The Arctic ice cap is melting from global warming because of the combustion of fossil fuels, and entrepreneurs, rather than rushing to find solutions, are rushing to drill for more oil.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I cannot believe what I am reading. The Arctic ice cap is melting from global warming because of the combustion of fossil fuels, and entrepreneurs, rather than rushing to find solutions, are rushing to drill for more oil.</p>
        <p>I feel that I am going insane in an insane world.</p>
        <p>Graham Marks  Alfred, N.Y., Oct. 10, 2005</p>
      </block>
